-- cscope 
-- ctags

-- cscope -R
-- ctags -R

i - press i to insert text mode

esc - press esc key to come out of insert mode.


:w! save and dont' quit
:wq save and quit;
:wq!

:q! quit without saving;
:q

Ctrl + ] --> to open declaration of function;

Ctrl + o --> will take to previous location;

